    <span class="govuk-caption-xl gem-c-title__context">
      Press release
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    UK statement on Afghan peace talks
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">The UK welcomes progress in peace talks. The two sides have reached an agreement which will allow the start of more substantive negotiations to take place.</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
